data.description: DESIGNERS DREAM EARLY CENTURY WITH MODERN FLAIR. - home in McAlester, OK!  Hardwood flooring, and beams in ceilings, entry way, original front door, open living/dining, granite, stainless appliances, 2 pantries, 2 original cabinets from 1900's w/glass panes has been revived. All new paint, fixtures. Parquet original in den & rock fireplace, Primary bedroom features large bathroom with original 1900 century glass pane door's, claw foot tub, double sinks, granite and walk-in tiled shower! Hall bathroom is large with double mirrors original doors. Lots of storage in this stunning house. Basement, backyard has wood deck and one car garage, fire pit, wood and chain link fenced in yard and new landscaping! A must see!
